long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a new panel into your devtools to help you inspect elements styled by Styletron (works only when your application is built with NODE_ENV=development). Styletron is an universal toolkit for component-oriented styling. It falls into the CSS in JS category. It outputs performant Atomic CSS. However, that can be hard to debug since every rule lives in its own class. This extension adds a new panel that nicely merges styles into a single list. This feature works with styletron-react v5.1+ and styletron-engine-atomic v1.3+.
